WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:37.599 --> 00:01:38.359
What are you up to?

00:01:52.439 --> 00:01:53.760
Chen Yanyun.

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:56.599
You hide state secrets.

00:01:57.159 --> 00:01:58.560
That's treason.

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:03.439
Do you really think you can

00:02:03.719 --> 00:02:04.799
find the files in the Ji Mansion?

00:02:05.799 --> 00:02:07.359
I already had the files

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.319
sent to His Majesty at the palace.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:12.159
Yet you're willing to be a pawn

00:02:12.639 --> 00:02:13.960
at Fu Hailian's mercy.

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:16.080
Now you've been discarded.

00:02:16.240 --> 00:02:17.680
Your future is ruined.

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:19.680
By the laws of Great Yan,

00:02:20.120 --> 00:02:21.199
if a son accuses his father,

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.080
regardless of the father's crime,

00:02:23.719 --> 00:02:25.400
the son shall receive 40 cane strokes.

00:02:26.639 --> 00:02:28.240
I just lashed you 40 times.

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:29.639
Not one more,

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:30.639
not one less.

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.159
Since you sent word

00:02:41.159 --> 00:02:42.479
for me to come to Tongzhou,

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:44.439
I'll spare your life.

00:02:45.599 --> 00:02:47.479
I'll have you taken out of the capital.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.000
From now on,

00:02:50.159 --> 00:02:51.360
we are done with each other for good.

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:04.199
A grand councilor's nephew

00:03:05.439 --> 00:03:07.800
turns out to be a bandit's son.

00:03:10.840 --> 00:03:11.680
Deceiving the emperor,

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:13.000
for minor offenses,

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:15.039
stripped of all titles,

00:03:15.039 --> 00:03:15.759
for grave ones,

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:18.039
imprisonment or exile.

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.120
What's more,

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:26.120
he's also guilty of murder.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:54.680
Xuanqing.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:03:56.960
Chen Yi, hurry.
Fetch the doctor.

00:03:57.919 --> 00:03:58.439
Yes.

00:03:59.039 --> 00:03:59.639
What did you do?

00:04:01.120 --> 00:04:02.159
No need.

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:07.000
You swallowed poison.
Spit it out.

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:16.639
I didn't want you dead.

00:04:16.639 --> 00:04:17.800
Why do this?

00:04:25.079 --> 00:04:26.199
Uncle,

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:29.560
I've always admired you.

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:36.920
Ever since I was little,

00:04:39.959 --> 00:04:41.800
I've tried to emulate you in everything.

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:45.519
But I've always hesitated,

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.759
lingering in indecision.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.519
I've long fallen for her, yet only

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:52.040
wished to become someone like you.

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:53.560
I thought
someday

00:04:54.519 --> 00:04:56.560
I could have it all just like you.

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:59.079
But in the end I realized

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:01.319
I don't have half your clarity,

00:05:01.319 --> 00:05:02.079
not even a fraction.

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:04.480
Now my career,

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:05.680
love, life,

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:06.879
all ruined.

00:05:07.639 --> 00:05:09.639
One wrong step leads to endless regret.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:12.319
No need to save me.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:16.040
Xuanqing.

00:05:18.639 --> 00:05:19.319
Xuanqing.

00:06:48.879 --> 00:06:49.800
Why are you here?

00:06:55.399 --> 00:06:56.839
I heard from Yao

00:06:57.399 --> 00:06:58.480
that Xuanqing

00:07:02.319 --> 00:07:03.199
is dead.

00:07:04.360 --> 00:07:05.079
He came here

00:07:05.079 --> 00:07:06.519
resolved to die.

00:07:07.800 --> 00:07:09.240
He even took poison.

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:11.959
Fu Hailian pressured him over Yunting.

00:07:13.959 --> 00:07:14.680
What about Yunting?

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.399
Also dead.

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:20.160
Before I came,

00:07:20.519 --> 00:07:21.319
Shuntian Prefecture

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.879
already sent word to the manor,

00:07:23.959 --> 00:07:25.439
claiming it was an accidental drowning.

00:07:27.079 --> 00:07:29.319
I first met Xuanqing nine years ago.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.199
He was

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:35.839
thin and small,

00:07:35.959 --> 00:07:37.000
quiet and reserved.

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:39.839
His eyes

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:41.560
looked exactly like

00:07:41.560 --> 00:07:42.879
his birth father's.

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.000
Mother

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:18.639
wants to remove Xuanqing's name

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:20.600
from the family registry.

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:23.920
I'd like to hear your thoughts.

00:08:26.319 --> 00:08:27.439
It is

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:29.399
up to you.

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:41.480
Fine.

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:55.120
Sir,

00:08:55.720 --> 00:08:56.240
Chen Yi,

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:57.360
Chen Yanyun's man, just came.

00:08:57.519 --> 00:08:58.200
He said Chen Yanyun

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:59.240
has a message for you.
What is it?

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:01.679
Chen Xuanqing failed.

00:09:01.799 --> 00:09:02.720
He took poison and died.

00:09:06.159 --> 00:09:06.759
Sir,

00:09:07.519 --> 00:09:09.080
what do you think

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.559
Chen Yanyun means by this?

00:09:10.960 --> 00:09:11.759
Is he

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:13.279
trying to threaten you?

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.240
He's telling me

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:18.080
he's putting all the blame

00:09:18.080 --> 00:09:19.559
on me.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:20.759
He wouldn't dare.

00:09:21.799 --> 00:09:23.440
Should we get some censors

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:25.000
to make a case out of this?

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:25.879
After all,

00:09:26.240 --> 00:09:28.039
Chen Xuanqing died because of him.

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:29.000
Forget it.

00:09:30.279 --> 00:09:31.240
To defy me,

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.440
Chen Yanyun

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:34.919
has handed over all the case files

00:09:34.919 --> 00:09:36.720
hidden in the record office for a decade

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:39.000
to His Majesty.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:43.600
What a bold pledge of allegiance.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:46.480
Finally won His Majesty's trust.

00:09:47.240 --> 00:09:48.120
If I

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:49.759
press further now,

00:09:49.759 --> 00:09:51.639
I'll be going against His Majesty.

00:09:52.639 --> 00:09:53.480
But doesn't His Majesty

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.039
always heed your will?

00:09:59.080 --> 00:10:00.399
Watch your words.

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:02.600
Don't speak so recklessly again.

00:10:09.120 --> 00:10:10.399
Unless absolutely necessary,

00:10:10.679 --> 00:10:12.360
don't cross His Majesty.

00:10:13.679 --> 00:10:14.799
Forgive my loose tongue.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.799
You don't realize.

00:10:17.000 --> 00:10:19.159
His Majesty has grown up lately.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.200
Many in the court

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:23.879
await him to take power.

00:10:37.679 --> 00:10:39.279
Grandmother and I have discussed it.

00:10:39.799 --> 00:10:41.919
Our whole family, except me and Yanyun,

00:10:42.279 --> 00:10:44.840
will leave Tongzhou for a while.

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:46.440
Move to Songjiang Prefecture.

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:48.519
What?

00:10:49.159 --> 00:10:49.559
Why?

00:10:50.519 --> 00:10:51.519
Go all the way

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:53.000
to Songjiang?

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:54.440
Indeed.

00:10:54.759 --> 00:10:55.480
We do have

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.120
some business

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:58.320
in Songjiang.

00:10:58.600 --> 00:10:59.559
But our main ventures

00:10:59.759 --> 00:11:01.120
are all in the north.

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:03.679
If we all move to Songjiang,

00:11:04.039 --> 00:11:05.159
we'll lose hold of

00:11:05.279 --> 00:11:06.480
our northern business.

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:07.080
Mother.

00:11:07.679 --> 00:11:08.799
I can travel back and forth.

00:11:08.799 --> 00:11:09.320
You…

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:11.000
You already knew about this?

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:12.519
How could you not
say a word

00:11:13.480 --> 00:11:14.799
about something so important?

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:15.679
Alright.

00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:17.440
Since

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:19.480
Jinzhao and Yanyun have said so,

00:11:19.559 --> 00:11:21.519
we'll do as told.

00:11:21.840 --> 00:11:23.960
It pains me to

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.080
make you all leave your home.

00:11:26.679 --> 00:11:27.440
I offer my sincere apology

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:31.759
to you all.

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:33.000
Yanyun.

00:11:33.159 --> 00:11:34.559
Please don't say that.

00:11:35.039 --> 00:11:36.120
Your humble apology

00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:38.799
puts me to shame.

00:11:39.039 --> 00:11:39.960
Please be seated.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:49.600
You know

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:51.279
the Ji Mansion's

00:11:51.279 --> 00:11:53.279
prosperity today

00:11:53.879 --> 00:11:56.440
is all thanks to Yanyun's care.

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:58.440
And this move to Songjiang,

00:11:58.639 --> 00:12:01.000
he's doing it for our good.

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:05.720
Yes, yes.

00:12:06.399 --> 00:12:07.840
After all,

00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:09.240
we're family.

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:11.639
Aunt.

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:13.000
Uncle.

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:15.879
Yanyun truly feels

00:12:15.879 --> 00:12:16.919
he has wronged our family.

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:18.879
Jinzhao is right.

00:12:19.279 --> 00:12:20.799
Ever since I placed

00:12:20.799 --> 00:12:22.000
those case files here,

00:12:22.559 --> 00:12:23.720
I've put

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:25.360
your entire household

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:26.679
on the line of fire.

00:12:27.399 --> 00:12:29.399
The feud between

00:12:29.399 --> 00:12:30.519
Fu Hailian and me

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.679
has nearly brought ruin to the family.

00:12:33.159 --> 00:12:34.480
I still tremble at the thought.

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:35.840
Relations

00:12:35.840 --> 00:12:37.039
between Fu Hailian and I

00:12:37.679 --> 00:12:38.279
will only

00:12:38.519 --> 00:12:40.039
grow worse.

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:41.840
Thus I beg Madam Ji to

00:12:42.159 --> 00:12:44.320
take you to Songjiang and lie low.

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:47.799
I don't want to leave.

00:12:48.559 --> 00:12:49.720
If the capital is dangerous,

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:51.000
and Jinzhao stays,
I want to stay too.

00:12:52.759 --> 00:12:53.559
Don't be willful.

00:12:54.159 --> 00:12:54.799
Sit down.

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:57.559
Given the situation,

00:12:57.799 --> 00:12:59.120
only if you move to Songjiang

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:00.759
can I feel at ease.

00:13:02.159 --> 00:13:03.799
You've already decided,

00:13:04.799 --> 00:13:06.080
why ask for our opinions now?

00:13:10.279 --> 00:13:11.320
Should I address you

00:13:11.320 --> 00:13:12.120
as Mr. Chen
or brother-in-law?

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:14.799
Now I ask you,

00:13:15.759 --> 00:13:16.960
my brother-in-law, I wanna

00:13:17.919 --> 00:13:19.519
take my sister to Songjiang with me,

00:13:19.759 --> 00:13:20.600
is that okay with you?

00:13:20.879 --> 00:13:22.360
Why ask him?

00:13:22.679 --> 00:13:23.840
You should ask me.

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:30.279
I won't go.

00:13:31.399 --> 00:13:32.600
Ask your brother-in-law

00:13:33.000 --> 00:13:34.320
if he can do without me.

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:36.799
Without me,

00:13:36.919 --> 00:13:37.960
he can't do anything.

00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:44.159
I swear to you all,

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:46.320
I will protect Jinzhao with my life.

00:13:46.799 --> 00:13:47.679
If any harm befalls her,

00:13:48.320 --> 00:13:49.120
I will lay down my life.

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:50.080
Yanyun,

00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:51.799
you don't have to say that.

00:13:53.759 --> 00:13:54.519
Ji Feng.

00:13:54.879 --> 00:13:55.480
Ma'am.

00:13:56.039 --> 00:13:57.360
Tell the servants

00:13:57.679 --> 00:13:59.360
to pack up immediately.

00:14:00.399 --> 00:14:00.840
Yes.

00:14:02.919 --> 00:14:03.840
You make it sound

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:05.200
as if I am the villain.

00:14:21.080 --> 00:14:23.639
Get everyone ready to depart.

00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:24.320
Yes.

00:14:26.720 --> 00:14:27.480
Jinzhao.

00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:29.840
You and Yanyun must be careful.

00:14:50.759 --> 00:14:52.039
After I see them off to Jining,

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.480
I'll return to the capital to help you.

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:54.879
Brother.

00:14:55.039 --> 00:14:56.120
I agreed to go to Songjiang

00:14:56.120 --> 00:14:57.519
to put my mother's mind at ease.

00:14:58.080 --> 00:14:59.000
Don't try to persuade me.

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:01.000
I cannot bear
to leave you alone

00:15:02.679 --> 00:15:03.799
here in the capital.

00:15:05.240 --> 00:15:06.519
I have Yanyun with me.

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:07.600
Precisely because he is here,

00:15:07.600 --> 00:15:08.840
I worry all the more.

00:15:10.320 --> 00:15:11.200
Enough talk.

00:15:11.480 --> 00:15:12.279
It's decided.

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:29.919
What's wrong?

00:15:30.440 --> 00:15:31.399
Yao says he'll

00:15:31.679 --> 00:15:33.360
stay in the capital to help us.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:45.919
Chen Yanyun lacks moral integrity,

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:47.120
and brings unrest to his household,

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:48.440
unworthy of his post as court minister.

00:15:48.840 --> 00:15:51.279
He abuses power in court and indulges in debauchery,

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:53.240
defying all ethics and honor,

00:15:53.360 --> 00:15:54.440
colludes with merchants,

00:15:54.519 --> 00:15:56.960
forms factions, deceives Your Majesty.

00:15:57.159 --> 00:15:58.120
I beg Your Majesty

00:15:58.440 --> 00:16:00.960
to thoroughly investigate his misdeeds.

00:16:04.519 --> 00:16:05.559
Yanyun.

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:07.320
Yanyun.

00:16:39.480 --> 00:16:40.399
Chen Yanyun.

00:16:41.919 --> 00:16:43.519
Don't you dare leave me.

00:16:47.279 --> 00:16:48.200
I won't leave you.

00:16:48.600 --> 00:16:49.200
I'm right here.

00:16:49.679 --> 00:16:50.360
Always will be.

00:16:55.159 --> 00:16:55.720
It's alright.

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:19.720
Why are we at Baoxiang Temple?

00:17:19.880 --> 00:17:20.440
You're awake.

00:17:21.200 --> 00:17:22.279
Put me down.

00:17:22.279 --> 00:17:23.400
I can walk on my own.

00:17:24.599 --> 00:17:25.440
Stay still.

00:17:26.279 --> 00:17:27.599
I simply wish to carry you.

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.960
This is a temple after all.

00:17:32.519 --> 00:17:33.759
I believe the Buddha

00:17:34.799 --> 00:17:36.400
blesses true love between mortals.

00:17:39.559 --> 00:17:40.200
That's right.
Jinzhao,

00:17:41.920 --> 00:17:43.559
you should smile like that more often.

00:17:46.599 --> 00:17:47.960
As long as we're both safe and well,

00:17:48.440 --> 00:17:49.799
I'll be happy every day.

00:17:52.559 --> 00:17:53.640
I'm sorry, Jinzhao.

00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:58.240
Why do you apologize?

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.359
Your family

00:18:03.759 --> 00:18:05.160
dote on you so deeply,

00:18:07.079 --> 00:18:07.920
but what I do

00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:09.279
isn't even a fraction of that.

00:18:10.599 --> 00:18:11.680
Those concerns you had

00:18:11.680 --> 00:18:12.640
before marrying me

00:18:13.319 --> 00:18:14.680
were absolutely right.

00:18:16.079 --> 00:18:16.839
What's this about?

00:18:17.279 --> 00:18:17.839
Are you thinking

00:18:17.839 --> 00:18:19.319
of bringing out the divorce paper

00:18:19.680 --> 00:18:20.400
and letting me go?

00:18:22.759 --> 00:18:23.640
Not a chance.

00:18:24.799 --> 00:18:26.200
Without you,

00:18:27.079 --> 00:18:28.599
I can't do anything.

00:18:30.200 --> 00:18:31.240
Stop it.

00:18:35.720 --> 00:18:36.440
Fine.

00:18:40.599 --> 00:18:42.000
If we could start over,

00:18:42.160 --> 00:18:43.440
would you still marry me?

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:45.559
Even earlier.

00:18:56.759 --> 00:18:57.359
We're here.

00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:14.000
Mr. Chen.

00:19:14.119 --> 00:19:15.160
A distinguished guest has arrived.

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:21.559
Understood.

00:19:24.880 --> 00:19:25.880
I'll be right back.

00:19:42.839 --> 00:19:43.640
Don't catch a chill.

00:19:49.880 --> 00:19:51.400
Please come in.

00:19:58.839 --> 00:20:01.079
The Second Prince of the northern steppe
has killed his brother and seized the throne.

00:20:01.480 --> 00:20:03.400
Rebels have stormed the trading town of Shi City,

00:20:03.559 --> 00:20:05.160
and injured many Great Yan citizens.

00:20:05.599 --> 00:20:06.720
The military dispatch

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:07.680
arrived by express courier

00:20:07.799 --> 00:20:09.039
has everyone worried about border unrest.

00:20:09.160 --> 00:20:11.039
Yet Fu Hailian remains unruffled,

00:20:11.400 --> 00:20:12.000
For days now, he has offered

00:20:12.000 --> 00:20:13.160
no proper solution. He even claims

00:20:13.759 --> 00:20:16.880
the situation is well under control,

00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:18.839
telling me not to worry.

00:20:19.720 --> 00:20:20.559
In my view, he's already

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:22.559
colluding with the Northern Barbarians.

00:20:23.400 --> 00:20:26.279
His proposals to cut military spending

00:20:26.279 --> 00:20:27.400
and reduce border garrisons,

00:20:27.880 --> 00:20:29.480
all meant to stir trouble at the frontier,

00:20:30.039 --> 00:20:30.680
forcing me

00:20:30.799 --> 00:20:32.079
to rely on him again,

00:20:33.039 --> 00:20:35.480
so he can keep a tight grip on power.

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:37.079
Your Majesty's speculation

00:20:37.079 --> 00:20:38.079
is not unfounded.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:39.720
But

00:20:40.519 --> 00:20:41.920
there's no hard evidence.

00:20:42.440 --> 00:20:43.599
After all he has done to you,

00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:44.599
you still defend him?

00:20:44.839 --> 00:20:45.400
I am not

00:20:46.039 --> 00:20:47.400
defending him.

00:20:48.160 --> 00:20:48.920
It's just...

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:51.599
He's the foremost civil official.

00:20:52.039 --> 00:20:53.440
Without conclusive proof

00:20:53.680 --> 00:20:54.640
to condemn him

00:20:55.319 --> 00:20:56.880
will stir court chaos at the least,

00:20:57.240 --> 00:20:57.960
at worst, it will

00:20:58.680 --> 00:20:59.720
shake the foundation of the realm.

00:21:01.359 --> 00:21:02.079
Then we shall investigate.

00:21:02.799 --> 00:21:03.480
I intend to

00:21:04.319 --> 00:21:05.759
send an envoy to congratulate

00:21:06.960 --> 00:21:08.799
the Second Prince on his ascension,

00:21:09.119 --> 00:21:10.920
and to probe the border situation.

00:21:11.680 --> 00:21:12.799
What do you think, Chen Yanyun?

00:21:15.279 --> 00:21:16.119
Your Majesty,

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.559
that is an excellent plan.

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:19.640
Even Fu Hailian

00:21:19.799 --> 00:21:21.240
could not object.

00:21:21.720 --> 00:21:22.759
However,

00:21:22.759 --> 00:21:24.440
the choice of envoy stumps me.

00:21:25.319 --> 00:21:26.240
There are few

00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:28.319
I can truly trust

00:21:28.599 --> 00:21:29.519
in the entire court.

00:21:39.039 --> 00:21:39.640
Your Majesty.

00:21:40.440 --> 00:21:41.519
He's not the right choice.

00:21:42.799 --> 00:21:43.519
Why?

00:21:46.160 --> 00:21:47.279
Because I intend to go.

00:21:51.400 --> 00:21:51.960
You?

00:21:53.799 --> 00:21:54.960
You are not qualified enough.

00:21:55.880 --> 00:21:57.400
As the heir of Lord Changxing

00:21:57.640 --> 00:21:58.920
and Commander of the Xuanfeng Guard,

00:21:59.160 --> 00:22:00.279
I'm more qualified than you.

00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:02.400
Don't forget,

00:22:02.599 --> 00:22:03.519
you currently

00:22:04.000 --> 00:22:05.359
hold no official post.

00:22:06.160 --> 00:22:07.960
Precisely because of that,

00:22:08.319 --> 00:22:10.079
His Majesty has reason to send me.

00:22:10.960 --> 00:22:12.759
Those with official duties

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:14.240
dare not take this mission.

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:15.799
And those who dare

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:18.119
cannot get the job done.

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:23.599
Your Majesty.

00:22:23.839 --> 00:22:25.640
I understand your intention.

00:22:25.839 --> 00:22:26.640
But

00:22:27.039 --> 00:22:28.359
may I humbly ask Your Majesty

00:22:28.799 --> 00:22:29.559
to allow me

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.720
to consult my wife first?

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:32.880
What?

00:22:33.319 --> 00:22:34.400
It's a matter of state.

00:22:34.799 --> 00:22:36.200
You cannot decide for yourself?

00:22:36.440 --> 00:22:37.960
It's a fine chance for your reinstatement.

00:22:38.160 --> 00:22:38.759
I can

00:22:39.279 --> 00:22:40.880
make the decision myself.

00:22:41.359 --> 00:22:42.039
But

00:22:42.319 --> 00:22:43.599
I once nearly brought ruin

00:22:43.799 --> 00:22:45.839
upon the entire Ji household.

00:22:46.680 --> 00:22:47.319
I already

00:22:47.839 --> 00:22:49.440
owe Jinzhao a great apology.

00:22:50.039 --> 00:22:51.640
We both know full well

00:22:51.720 --> 00:22:52.359
what lies

00:22:52.680 --> 00:22:54.519
behind the border unrest.

00:22:55.039 --> 00:22:56.160
An envoy to the northern steppe

00:22:56.759 --> 00:22:58.000
will face great peril.

00:22:58.440 --> 00:22:59.119
I must

00:22:59.839 --> 00:23:01.200
speak plainly to my wife.

00:23:03.119 --> 00:23:03.640
Fine.

00:23:04.079 --> 00:23:05.400
Bring Gu Jinzhao here.

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:07.279
No need for you to explain.

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:08.359
I'll persuade her myself.

00:23:11.079 --> 00:23:12.119
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:23:18.440 --> 00:23:19.400
You asked His Majesty to protect

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:21.599
the Ji family from any fallout.

00:23:21.599 --> 00:23:23.079
That's fine.

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:25.319
But you also

00:23:25.640 --> 00:23:27.200
asked for three hundred muskets.

00:23:28.359 --> 00:23:29.200
Do you know

00:23:29.599 --> 00:23:31.319
that of these new muskets,

00:23:31.720 --> 00:23:32.920
the entire arsenal

00:23:33.119 --> 00:23:35.160
only has three hundred?

00:23:35.640 --> 00:23:37.920
Lords Jingyuan and Wuqing

00:23:37.920 --> 00:23:39.000
have long coveted them

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:40.519
yet not one was granted.

00:23:40.759 --> 00:23:41.640
That's exactly why

00:23:42.039 --> 00:23:43.079
you cannot ask for

00:23:43.319 --> 00:23:44.640
something like this.

00:23:45.119 --> 00:23:46.960
Only a naive woman like me

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:48.519
can make such an outrageous demand.

00:23:49.440 --> 00:23:51.119
You'll take all those muskets

00:23:51.400 --> 00:23:52.279
with you.

00:23:53.319 --> 00:23:54.079
Indeed.

00:23:54.559 --> 00:23:55.599
Thanks to you, Jinzhao.

00:23:56.839 --> 00:23:57.720
If not for you,

00:23:57.880 --> 00:23:59.519
I would have been at a loss again.

00:24:00.079 --> 00:24:01.160
At a loss?

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:02.599
Nonsense.

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:04.160
Don't think I don't know.

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:05.720
You have long been eager to go.

00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:08.400
The Chunyuan remnants are all there.

00:24:08.480 --> 00:24:09.400
You are anxious

00:24:09.400 --> 00:24:11.200
to gather evidence against Fu Hailian.

00:24:16.200 --> 00:24:16.799
Yeah.

00:24:18.599 --> 00:24:19.400
I do hope

00:24:20.119 --> 00:24:21.880
to find proof of his crimes.

00:24:22.480 --> 00:24:23.400
Yet truth be told,

00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:26.000
I would rather find none at all.

00:24:32.079 --> 00:24:33.039
I know,

00:24:33.759 --> 00:24:34.640
deep down,

00:24:35.519 --> 00:24:37.039
you still cherish

00:24:37.039 --> 00:24:38.519
your bond as teacher and student.

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:40.720
But

00:24:41.519 --> 00:24:42.960
he feels no such regard for you.

00:24:46.400 --> 00:24:48.000
If you journey to the northern steppe,

00:24:48.799 --> 00:24:49.960
he will surely lay

00:24:49.960 --> 00:24:51.319
a deadly trap

00:24:51.519 --> 00:24:52.319
waiting for you.

00:25:01.640 --> 00:25:02.960
Why not go pray at the temple?

00:25:05.920 --> 00:25:07.160
In such grave matters,

00:25:07.960 --> 00:25:09.039
I would rather trust you

00:25:09.680 --> 00:25:10.440
and myself,

00:25:11.119 --> 00:25:12.319
not gods or Buddhas.

00:25:31.160 --> 00:25:31.799
I bid you farewell,

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:33.359
master.

00:25:34.079 --> 00:25:35.799
The road ahead is long and distant,

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:38.039
take care of yourself.

00:25:39.400 --> 00:25:40.440
After this parting,

00:25:40.519 --> 00:25:41.759
we know not when we shall meet again.

00:25:42.200 --> 00:25:43.599
I have one question.

00:25:44.160 --> 00:25:45.240
Do you still remember

00:25:45.400 --> 00:25:46.720
after the metropolitan exam years ago

00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:48.000
when Fengming and I

00:25:48.240 --> 00:25:49.000
called at your residence

00:25:49.000 --> 00:25:50.079
to pay our respects?

00:25:53.359 --> 00:25:54.279
I do not recall.

00:25:54.680 --> 00:25:55.240
I suppose not.

00:25:55.880 --> 00:25:57.640
You were not home that day.

00:25:58.640 --> 00:25:59.839
Yet Fengming and I

00:26:00.759 --> 00:26:01.599
knew nothing of it.

00:26:02.079 --> 00:26:03.240
After breakfast that morning,

00:26:03.480 --> 00:26:04.920
we went straight to your manor.

00:26:05.039 --> 00:26:06.480
We waited 6 full hours

00:26:06.960 --> 00:26:08.440
before being shown to the side hall.

00:26:08.640 --> 00:26:10.519
We never got to see you in the end,

00:26:10.799 --> 00:26:12.960
but were given a policy essay to write.

00:26:16.920 --> 00:26:18.880
I seem to have faint recollection.

00:26:20.240 --> 00:26:22.119
After finishing the essay,

00:26:22.640 --> 00:26:23.680
I returned home only to find

00:26:23.799 --> 00:26:25.039
the moon already high in the sky.

00:26:25.920 --> 00:26:27.240
I slept less than 4 hours

00:26:27.920 --> 00:26:29.119
before Mother woke me at dawn

00:26:29.640 --> 00:26:30.279
and said an invitation

00:26:30.279 --> 00:26:31.880
had arrived from your mansion,

00:26:32.319 --> 00:26:33.440
asking me to come again early in the morning.

00:26:33.680 --> 00:26:35.400
I still remember clearly to this day

00:26:36.119 --> 00:26:37.319
the first words you spoke to me

00:26:37.519 --> 00:26:38.519
when we met.

00:26:38.799 --> 00:26:39.359
You said,

00:26:39.680 --> 00:26:40.599
Chen Yanyun,

00:26:41.960 --> 00:26:42.880
you ought to have failed

00:26:43.400 --> 00:26:44.599
the metropolitan exam.

00:26:50.319 --> 00:26:52.000
I said that?

00:26:52.599 --> 00:26:53.440
You also said

00:26:53.720 --> 00:26:54.960
the reason you

00:26:55.240 --> 00:26:56.039
failed me

00:26:56.960 --> 00:26:58.799
was because of the essay I wrote

00:26:58.799 --> 00:27:00.079
during the exam.

00:27:00.880 --> 00:27:02.279
It was far too accurate.

00:27:02.920 --> 00:27:03.839
Not well-written.

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:05.119
But far too accurate.

00:27:07.440 --> 00:27:08.240
Back then,

00:27:09.240 --> 00:27:11.079
you were set on promoting new policies,

00:27:11.759 --> 00:27:13.240
yet had very few supporters.

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:16.240
The content of my essay

00:27:16.920 --> 00:27:18.240
matched exactly

00:27:18.240 --> 00:27:19.160
what was in your heart.

00:27:19.519 --> 00:27:20.759
Thus you thought

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:22.039
I was either

00:27:22.759 --> 00:27:24.240
unusually wise

00:27:24.480 --> 00:27:25.599
or far too skilled

00:27:26.039 --> 00:27:27.519
at reading others' minds.

00:27:27.839 --> 00:27:29.119
And you have never liked

00:27:29.799 --> 00:27:31.160
that kind of person.

00:27:33.119 --> 00:27:34.240
Even to this day,

00:27:35.240 --> 00:27:36.640
I still don't.

00:27:39.880 --> 00:27:42.039
Do you still remember

00:27:42.319 --> 00:27:43.920
the policy essay

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:45.279
you set for me alone?

00:27:47.160 --> 00:27:48.519
The topic was

00:27:48.680 --> 00:27:50.039
the rise and fall of reform,

00:27:50.640 --> 00:27:52.000
and the gains and faults of the new policies.

00:27:52.839 --> 00:27:54.400
I wrote five full pages.

00:27:54.960 --> 00:27:56.119
But in the end, you told me

00:27:56.480 --> 00:27:58.599
the whole lengthy essay

00:27:59.319 --> 00:28:01.039
boiled down to just eight words.

00:28:02.440 --> 00:28:03.720
"For the people's benefit,"

00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:05.960
"regardless of personal cost."

00:28:09.119 --> 00:28:10.200
From that day on,

00:28:11.599 --> 00:28:12.400
those eight words

00:28:12.400 --> 00:28:13.519
have been carved into my mind

00:28:13.519 --> 00:28:14.799
and printed on my heart.

00:28:18.559 --> 00:28:19.960
What exactly are you trying to say?

00:28:23.319 --> 00:28:24.000
Sir,

00:28:26.279 --> 00:28:27.880
Fengming is dead.

00:28:31.400 --> 00:28:32.440
Once,

00:28:34.519 --> 00:28:35.960
for the sake of the new policies,

00:28:35.960 --> 00:28:37.960
for land equalization, for you,

00:28:39.319 --> 00:28:40.559
we were willing to die.

00:28:43.359 --> 00:28:44.559
But now look

00:28:49.720 --> 00:28:50.519
what has become

00:28:50.519 --> 00:28:51.799
of it all.

00:29:51.759 --> 00:29:52.680
I bathed

00:29:53.839 --> 00:29:54.920
in the grace of your teachings,

00:29:56.000 --> 00:29:57.079
and received your kindness as a master.

00:29:57.920 --> 00:29:59.319
I hold this debt deep in my heart

00:29:59.319 --> 00:30:00.200
and know not how to repay it.

00:30:02.279 --> 00:30:03.319
I only beg you

00:30:05.319 --> 00:30:06.720
to stay true.

00:31:50.200 --> 00:31:51.240
He's long gone.

00:31:51.799 --> 00:31:52.799
Why linger here still?

00:31:57.759 --> 00:31:58.880
I just

00:31:59.680 --> 00:32:00.960
need some time to myself.

00:32:07.680 --> 00:32:08.920
You don't need to worry about him.

00:32:09.319 --> 00:32:10.240
On this mission to the northern steppe,

00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:11.880
he knows full well Fu Hailian

00:32:11.880 --> 00:32:12.960
will move against him.

00:32:13.599 --> 00:32:15.119
So he openly broke with him

00:32:15.119 --> 00:32:16.240
before the entire court.

00:32:17.640 --> 00:32:19.279
This way, if Fu Hailian tries

00:32:19.759 --> 00:32:20.519
to harm the envoy party,

00:32:20.519 --> 00:32:21.799
it'll look like

00:32:22.400 --> 00:32:23.880
nothing but personal vengeance.

00:32:25.640 --> 00:32:26.599
Your husband

00:32:26.839 --> 00:32:27.880
is deep and calculating.

00:32:28.599 --> 00:32:29.440
He will not be outwitted.

00:32:35.079 --> 00:32:35.880
Thank you.

00:32:36.720 --> 00:32:37.599
What for?

00:32:39.279 --> 00:32:40.480
For comforting me.

00:32:42.279 --> 00:32:43.200
I am doing no such thing.

00:33:14.880 --> 00:33:15.799
All of you, step down.

00:33:36.079 --> 00:33:37.039
I've heard

00:33:37.559 --> 00:33:38.960
before the envoy's departure,

00:33:39.759 --> 00:33:41.759
Chen Yanyun openly rebuked you

00:33:42.599 --> 00:33:43.960
and cut off all ties with you.

00:33:47.880 --> 00:33:50.559
He did that on purpose.

00:33:54.960 --> 00:33:56.720
Truly a clever ploy.

00:33:59.720 --> 00:34:01.039
Yet what does it matter?

00:34:01.599 --> 00:34:03.880
No matter what schemes he lays,

00:34:04.720 --> 00:34:06.759
he will never return from this journey.

00:34:09.760 --> 00:34:11.119
Is everything arranged?

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:18.599
Good.

00:34:22.079 --> 00:34:23.119
Good.

00:34:25.440 --> 00:34:27.280
If not for fear he might dig deeper

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:29.559
and uncover the Chunyuan Sect,

00:34:29.559 --> 00:34:30.599
I would never

00:34:31.639 --> 00:34:33.880
have sought his life.

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:36.039
What a pity.

00:34:42.360 --> 00:34:43.960
I once truly considered

00:34:45.679 --> 00:34:47.320
letting him take my place.

00:34:53.199 --> 00:34:54.840
Pity.

00:35:05.280 --> 00:35:06.760
I'm heading to Western Hills tomorrow.

00:35:07.039 --> 00:35:07.960
Take charge of Baopu

00:35:08.400 --> 00:35:09.119
while I am gone.

00:35:10.119 --> 00:35:10.800
Alright.

00:35:11.920 --> 00:35:12.760
I didn't expect

00:35:12.760 --> 00:35:14.360
you'd gotten this fat.

00:35:18.440 --> 00:35:19.079
Thanks.

00:35:21.039 --> 00:35:22.159
For what?

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:24.119
I still have things to do

00:35:24.440 --> 00:35:25.320
in the office.

00:35:36.440 --> 00:35:37.000
Hey.

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:38.519
We had a deal.

00:35:42.239 --> 00:35:43.639
Keep Gu Jinzhao company for a few days.

00:35:44.719 --> 00:35:45.440
You're backing out again.

00:35:48.400 --> 00:35:49.360
It was me

00:35:49.360 --> 00:35:50.519
who took care of you.

00:35:50.880 --> 00:35:52.800
I fed you for so long.

00:35:53.639 --> 00:35:55.159
Just a few days with Ye Xian

00:35:55.360 --> 00:35:56.320
and you've turned into this?

00:35:57.079 --> 00:35:58.800
Such an ungrateful cat.

00:35:59.400 --> 00:35:59.920
Hey.

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:00.960
What did you say?

00:36:01.599 --> 00:36:03.000
How could you say that to a cat?

00:36:07.119 --> 00:36:07.719
Madam.

00:36:11.639 --> 00:36:12.400
Sir.

00:36:14.280 --> 00:36:15.360
Urgent secret report just arrived.

00:36:16.159 --> 00:36:18.159
The envoy party was ambushed in Shi City.

00:36:19.039 --> 00:36:20.440
Only two men made it back to the capital.

00:36:21.119 --> 00:36:22.079
Overnight,

00:36:22.880 --> 00:36:24.159
all the others vanished without a trace.

00:36:27.320 --> 00:36:27.960
What?

00:36:29.119 --> 00:36:30.039
What about him?

00:36:31.199 --> 00:36:32.320
Mr. Chen

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.400
is also missing.

00:36:41.280 --> 00:36:41.920
Gu Jinzhao.

00:36:47.079 --> 00:36:47.760
I'm fine.

00:36:50.000 --> 00:36:51.440
As expected.

00:36:55.880 --> 00:36:56.519
Do you recall

00:36:56.519 --> 00:36:57.639
the names of the two who returned?

00:36:58.239 --> 00:36:58.920
Yes.

00:36:59.599 --> 00:37:00.639
They are from the Censorate:

00:37:00.880 --> 00:37:02.599
Lin Ruhui and Zhou Chudong.

00:37:04.519 --> 00:37:06.079
I know those two.

00:37:07.400 --> 00:37:09.119
They are Fu Hailian's men.

00:37:10.960 --> 00:37:12.119
It seems

00:37:12.599 --> 00:37:14.159
Fu Hailian's next move

00:37:15.039 --> 00:37:16.639
is to strike at the entire Chen Manor.

00:37:19.159 --> 00:37:20.119
Logically speaking,

00:37:20.320 --> 00:37:21.639
with the envoy ambushed,

00:37:22.079 --> 00:37:23.400
Yanyun is presumed dead.

00:37:24.079 --> 00:37:25.360
But if Fu Hailian means to

00:37:25.360 --> 00:37:26.800
destroy the Chen household,

00:37:27.199 --> 00:37:29.280
he will fabricate blame for the ambush

00:37:29.719 --> 00:37:31.719
and pin it entirely on Yanyun.

00:37:40.079 --> 00:37:41.159
I see!

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:51.719
I want to see His Majesty.

00:37:53.079 --> 00:37:53.599
Okay.

00:37:54.079 --> 00:37:54.719
I'll arrange it.

00:37:57.280 --> 00:37:58.960
The weather is dry,

00:37:59.119 --> 00:38:00.920
be careful with fire.

00:38:01.360 --> 00:38:03.039
The weather is dry,

00:38:03.199 --> 00:38:05.119
be careful with fire.

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:06.360
Even if you had not come to me,

00:38:06.719 --> 00:38:08.039
I would have sent for you.

00:38:08.920 --> 00:38:09.800
Two censors

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:11.119
have fled back from Shi City.

00:38:11.719 --> 00:38:13.440
They bring a letter from

00:38:13.440 --> 00:38:14.679
the Second Prince addressed to Yanyun.

00:38:15.360 --> 00:38:17.400
It proves he colluded with the Northern Barbarians

00:38:17.480 --> 00:38:18.480
to ambush the envoy party.

00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:21.280
The court ministers insist the entire

00:38:21.719 --> 00:38:23.760
Chen household be imprisoned and investigated.

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:24.960
Your Majesty,

00:38:25.440 --> 00:38:27.000
Yanyun is innocent.

00:38:28.800 --> 00:38:29.840
I know that full well.

00:38:30.760 --> 00:38:32.320
My hidden spies

00:38:32.960 --> 00:38:33.599
have sent word:

00:38:34.119 --> 00:38:35.480
after the ambush,

00:38:35.840 --> 00:38:37.079
he had every chance to escape.

00:38:39.239 --> 00:38:39.800
Liang,

00:38:40.360 --> 00:38:41.920
I'm putting the envoy party in your hands.

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:43.880
Shi City is ringed by mountains.

00:38:44.239 --> 00:38:45.239
Once you flee,

00:38:45.320 --> 00:38:46.280
find a place to lie low.

00:38:46.679 --> 00:38:47.760
Let both the imperial court and the northern steppe

00:38:47.760 --> 00:38:49.519
believe the envoy party has perished entirely.

00:38:49.880 --> 00:38:50.519
Only then

00:38:50.519 --> 00:38:51.960
will we minimize the danger.

00:38:52.159 --> 00:38:52.679
Chen Yi,
you stay with them

00:38:53.519 --> 00:38:54.559
and protect Liang.

00:38:54.800 --> 00:38:56.039
Yes, sir.

00:38:57.079 --> 00:38:57.960
But after that,

00:38:58.519 --> 00:38:59.679
no more news came.

00:39:01.719 --> 00:39:02.800
No news

00:39:03.400 --> 00:39:04.679
is better than bad news.

00:39:07.280 --> 00:39:08.239
Thank you, Your Majesty,

00:39:08.639 --> 00:39:10.039
for telling me this.

00:39:10.920 --> 00:39:11.800
The greatest trouble now

00:39:12.559 --> 00:39:13.639
is that letter

00:39:13.719 --> 00:39:14.840
allegedly exchanged

00:39:14.840 --> 00:39:16.280
with the Second Prince.

00:39:17.079 --> 00:39:18.639
With Yanyun missing,

00:39:18.960 --> 00:39:20.480
he has no way to defend himself.

00:39:21.519 --> 00:39:22.199
Your Majesty,

00:39:22.519 --> 00:39:24.199
I have a plan

00:39:24.519 --> 00:39:25.440
that can prove

00:39:25.800 --> 00:39:27.519
Yanyun would never betray you.

00:39:40.559 --> 00:39:41.639
What's this?

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:42.679
Last year,

00:39:42.840 --> 00:39:45.000
Yanyun told me you ordered

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:48.679
the arsenal to forge cannons,

00:39:49.039 --> 00:39:50.840
yet progress was slow.

00:39:51.519 --> 00:39:52.400
So he bade me send men

00:39:52.519 --> 00:39:54.159
to Macao to purchase them.

00:39:54.840 --> 00:39:55.960
Before Yanyun left,

00:39:56.280 --> 00:39:57.920
you bestowed upon me

00:39:57.920 --> 00:39:59.000
three hundred muskets.

00:39:59.480 --> 00:40:00.239
Now,

00:40:00.960 --> 00:40:02.320
I am willing to return them all

00:40:02.599 --> 00:40:03.840
to you, Your Majesty.

00:40:13.360 --> 00:40:15.599
One hundred small Farangi cannons,

00:40:15.880 --> 00:40:17.679
fifty large Farangi cannons,

00:40:18.119 --> 00:40:20.000
ten massive falcons,

00:40:20.639 --> 00:40:22.519
and ten cannon-making craftsmen.

00:40:23.199 --> 00:40:25.679
These were all purchased from Macao

00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:27.320
in the first half of the year

00:40:27.599 --> 00:40:28.960
and offered to me by Chen Yanyun.

00:40:29.239 --> 00:40:30.400
If he truly

00:40:30.519 --> 00:40:31.679
colluded with the Northern Barbarians,

00:40:32.280 --> 00:40:34.599
why would he have these cannons

00:40:34.840 --> 00:40:36.519
bought for me from afar?

00:40:37.119 --> 00:40:37.960
Shouldn't he have bought them

00:40:38.119 --> 00:40:39.760
for the Second Prince?

00:40:45.840 --> 00:40:46.679
In my view, the ones

00:40:46.760 --> 00:40:48.199
who should be strictly investigated

00:40:48.199 --> 00:40:49.920
are not the women and children

00:40:50.639 --> 00:40:52.880
of the Chen household,

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:54.280
but those two censors

00:40:54.440 --> 00:40:55.519
who escaped with their hides intact

00:40:55.519 --> 00:40:56.760
while the entire party went missing.

00:41:06.159 --> 00:41:06.960
Jinzhao.

00:41:07.320 --> 00:41:08.400
Are you really going to the border

00:41:08.400 --> 00:41:09.159
to find Yanyun?

00:41:11.320 --> 00:41:12.440
I don't trust the court.

00:41:13.920 --> 00:41:14.639
Besides,

00:41:15.079 --> 00:41:15.920
I sent Qingpu out

00:41:15.920 --> 00:41:17.039
a long time ago,

00:41:17.599 --> 00:41:18.719
and there's been no news.

00:41:19.559 --> 00:41:20.840
If I don't go myself,

00:41:21.079 --> 00:41:22.320
I can't rest easy.

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:26.039
Do not worry for me.

00:41:27.199 --> 00:41:28.400
I have business

00:41:28.679 --> 00:41:29.519
in Pingyang Prefecture.

00:41:29.760 --> 00:41:30.599
I have resources, I have people.

00:41:31.639 --> 00:41:32.599
I'll be fine.

00:41:33.840 --> 00:41:35.559
Then please be careful.

00:41:41.840 --> 00:41:43.239
After Mother heard the news,

00:41:43.239 --> 00:41:44.360
she took to her bed.

00:41:44.639 --> 00:41:45.719
She insisted on coming just now.

00:41:45.800 --> 00:41:47.320
It was no easy task calming her down.

00:41:50.400 --> 00:41:51.239
Are you truly

00:41:52.280 --> 00:41:53.400
resolved to go?

00:41:58.000 --> 00:41:58.679
Sis, these are

00:41:59.159 --> 00:42:00.559
the sacrificial fields

00:42:00.960 --> 00:42:02.039
Yanyun acquired over the years.

00:42:02.840 --> 00:42:05.159
No matter what happens,

00:42:05.480 --> 00:42:07.000
these lands will secure

00:42:07.480 --> 00:42:08.679
the family's livelihood

00:42:09.119 --> 00:42:10.079
without want.

00:42:20.480 --> 00:42:21.280
I understand.

00:42:22.280 --> 00:42:23.239
But I'm only

00:42:24.480 --> 00:42:26.199
keeping them for you temporarily.

00:42:27.320 --> 00:42:28.199
When you return,

00:42:28.440 --> 00:42:29.599
I'll give them back.

00:42:31.400 --> 00:42:32.400
Take the utmost care

00:42:32.599 --> 00:42:33.800
along the road.

00:42:34.159 --> 00:42:34.840
Okay?
Okay.

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:37.960
Thank you.

00:42:40.360 --> 00:42:41.519
Take care of yourself

00:42:42.480 --> 00:42:44.079
while looking for Yanyun.

00:42:44.960 --> 00:42:45.840
You too.

00:42:46.599 --> 00:42:47.760
Take care of yourself

00:42:47.920 --> 00:42:48.840
and Mother.

00:42:50.199 --> 00:42:51.519
I won't bid her formal farewell.

00:42:52.880 --> 00:42:53.599
Alright.

00:42:54.679 --> 00:42:55.480
Jinzhao,

00:42:57.719 --> 00:42:58.920
please stay safe.

00:43:01.039 --> 00:43:01.639
Take care.